hat makes a great centrepiece at any time of year</div></div></div></div></div><div class="recipe-header__bottom"><div class="recipe-header__share service-links__container"><div class="service-links"><div class="service-label">Share:</div><ul class="service-links-primary"><li class="service-links-facebook first"><a href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https%3A//www.bbcgoodfood.com/recipes/47615/creamed-leek-tart&amp;t=Creamed%20leek%20tart" title="Share on Facebook" class="service-links-facebook service-links-link" rel="nofollow" data-service-name="Facebook"><i class="font-icon font-icon-facebook-large"></i><span class="service-links-text">Facebook</span></a></li><li class="service-links-pinterest"><a href="http://pinterest.com/pin/create/bookmarklet?media=https%3A//www.bbcgoodfood.com/sites/default/files/recipe_images/recipe-image-legacy-id--90451_11.jpg&amp;url=https%3A//www.bbcgoodfood.com/recipes/47615/creamed-leek-tart&amp;title=Creamed%20leek%20tart&amp;is_video=false&amp;description=" title="Pin it on Pinterest" class="service-links-pinterest service-links-link" rel="nofollow" data-service-name="Pinterest"><i class="font-icon font-icon-pinterest-large"></i><span class="service-links-text">Pinterest</span></a></li><li class="service-links-twitter"><a href="http://twitter.com/share?url=https%3A//www.bbcgoodfood.com/recipes/47615/creamed-leek-tart&amp;text=Creamed%20leek%20tart" title="Share this on Twitter" class="service-links-twitter service-links-link" rel="nofollow" data-service-name="Twitter"><i class="font-icon font-icon-twitter-large"></i><span class="service-links-text">Twitter</span></a></li><li class="service-links-google-plus"><a href="https://plus.google.com/share?url=https%3A//www.bbcgoodfood.com/recipes/47615/creamed-leek-tart" title="Share this on Google+" class="service-links-google-plus service-links-link" rel="nofollow" data-service-name="Google+"><i class="font-icon font-icon-google-large"></i><span class="service-links-text">Google+</s