ow-make-ice-cream"><div class="vertical-push-item__image"> <span class="vertical-push-item__icon-overlay"></span> <img src="//www.bbcgoodfood.com/sites/default/files/styles/carousel_medium/public/technique_images/ice-cream-cms_0.jpg?itok=ykFj3Qh_" width="468" height="382" alt="How to make ice cream" title="How to make ice cream" /> <span class="vertical-push-item__badge vertical-push-item__badge--type">Video</span></div><h3 class="vertical-push-item__title"> How to make ice cream</h3> </a></article><article id="node-5410916" class="vertical-push-item vertical-push-item--carousel node node-guide-featured node-large-push-item clearfix"> <a href="/howto/guide/native/history-ice-cream"><div class="vertical-push-item__image"> <img src="//www.bbcgoodfood.com/sites/default/files/styles/carousel_medium/public/carte-hub.jpg?itok=A0AJ0G-B" width="468" height="382" alt="" /> <span class="vertical-push-item__badge vertical-push-item__badge--advertisement">Ad feature</span></div><h3 class="vertical-push-item__title"> The history of ice cream</h3><div class="vertical-push-item__text-content vertical-push-item__text-content--advertisement"> Advertisement feature</div> </a></article><article id="node-100017" class="vertical-push-item vertical-push-item--carousel node node-recipe node-large-push-item clearfix"> <a href="/recipes/1805644/chinese-roast-duck"><div class="vertical-push-item__image"> <img src="//www.bbcgoodfood.com/sites/default/files/styles/carousel_medium/public/recipe_images/recipe-image-legacy-id--837615_10.jpg?itok=HeWybRgg" width="468" height="382" alt="Chinese roast duck" title="Chinese roast duck" /> <span class="vertical-push-item__badge vertical-push-item__badge--type">Recipe</span></div><h3 class="vertical-push-item__title"> Chinese roast duck</h3><div class="push-item__ratings"><div class="clearfix fivestar-average-stars fivestar-average-text"><div class="fivestar-static-form-item"><div class="form-item form-type-item"><div class="field-main"><div class="five